reviewText: I also enjoy this season of Baywatch! It arrived on time and in new factory sealed, good working condition. Actress Donna D'Errico from Baywatch Nights became a regular cast member in this season. You also get to see Traci Bingham as Jordan Tate. And junior lifeguard Manny Guitterez, played by actor Jose Solano. This season 7 is the last year for actress Pamela Anderson and Yasmine Bleeth.
The product came on time. This is a great season of baywatch. The only problem is that don't have any subtitles.
